Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.96,0:20:34.51,Insert,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fade(380,380)}You are the only one for me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.09,0:20:40.80,Insert,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fade(380,380)}I can't remember your scent anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.80,0:20:47.85,Insert,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fade(380,380)}It's being washed away by the waves
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.82,0:21:04.12,Insert,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fade(380,380)}I'll go and grab hold of the rest of this dream, so wait for me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.12,0:21:10.33,Insert,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fade(380,380)}Before I realized it, I got too attached to your kindness to be alone again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.33,0:21:13.71,Insert,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fade(380,380)}Should I try to lift my flushed face?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.71,0:21:18.42,Insert,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fade(380,380)}I'm not alone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.42,0:21:20.51,Insert,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fade(380,380)}That's what I want
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.51,0:21:24.76,Insert,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fade(380,380)}That's what I want to believe
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.76,0:21:29.52,Insert,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fade(380,380)}Give it a shot
